1) Updated IPC training modules (to integrate risk com and rumours/misperception management) and updated messages on immunization, based on communication needs surrounding introduction of new vaccines in country (NoPV2, COVAX, HPV); 

2) Design of IEC and media materials

3) Mapping of feedback mechanisms for rumours and misinformation tracking and management (online and offline social platforms)
